                    <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/42994634/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/small/public/p42994634-1.jpg"></a>
                  </div>
                  <span class="">晨起鸟鸣，夜半钟声 明月惊鹊，清风鸣蝉 落霞孤鹜，秋水长天 疏影横斜，暗香浮动 月上柳梢，人约黄昏 松花酿酒，春水煎茶 ...... 这是古诗词中才会有的美和浪漫。 而今，我们想把古诗词里的浪漫和美，都展现在你的面前，于是有了“诗画系列”，有了《声律启蒙：吴冠中插图珍藏版》和《宋诗选：傅抱石插图珍藏版》。 文字之美，诗词之美，画意之美，以及画作vs文字所创造的意境之美，全在这套书中展现。对于孩子来说，这是一本发...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-04-10 14:19</span>
                  
                    &nbsp;&nbsp;<span class="">1人喜欢</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p> <span style="font-weight: bold;">晨起鸟鸣，夜半钟声</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">明月惊鹊，清风鸣蝉</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">落霞孤鹜，秋水长天</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">疏影横斜，暗香浮动</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">月上柳梢，人约黄昏</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">松花酿酒，春水煎茶</span></p><p>......</p><p>这是古诗词中才会有的美和浪漫。</p><p>而今，我们想把古诗词里的浪漫和美，都展现在你的面前，于是有了“诗画系列”，有了《声律启蒙：吴冠中插图珍藏版》和《宋诗选：傅抱石插图珍藏版》。</p><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">文字之美，诗词之美，画意之美，以及画作vs文字所创造的意境之美，全在这套书中展现。对于孩子来说，这是一本发现美、感知美的经典国学启蒙读物，即便对于大人，也是值得收藏的传统文学读物。</span>诗画系列书影拍摄 / 董佳</p><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-1.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">且温一壶闲酒，去重温那些遥远又温暖的日常温情</div></div></div><p> <span style="font-weight: bold;">特选的纸张，泛着淡淡的米黄色。</span> </p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-2.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">素雅精致的布面精装</div></div></div><p></p><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-3.jpg"></div></div><p></p><p></p><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-4.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">表面有一定的涂层，能够细腻地展现画作轻灵的细节，又能模拟宣纸的效果，读起来眼睛很舒服。</div></div></div><p></p><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-5.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">除此之外，特别邀请音乐人A.J. Alex &amp; Yan One为此书配乐，配乐采用古琴/古吉琴/拔弦小提琴/月吉琴/口风琴 等多种乐器，素材和灵感来自他们的最新行旅即兴唱片《柳三世》；朗读来自青年主播张晓雅（女声）、郭鹏超（男声），随书配套独家音频，扫描二维码，即可听配乐朗读。</div></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-5.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-6.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-6.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-7.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-7.jpg"></div><div class="image-caption-wrapper"><div class="image-caption">设计上选用竖排版，注释以红圈或者红日示意，模拟古人写书法的感觉</div></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-8.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-8.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img1.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-9.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-10.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center"><div class="image-wrapper"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/view/page_note/large/public/p42994634-12.jpg"></div></div><p></p><div class="image-container image-float-center">